    dc:description "Figs 2-6. Astochia africana (Ricardo). 2. Wing (Ruwenzori d') ca. 15 mm. 3. Female ovipositor (Lectotype-Mt. Kenya). 4-6. Male genitalia (Ruwenzori). 4. Lateral. 5. Dorsal aspect of clasper. 6. Ventral aspect, with claspers excluded." ;
